title: (Tues Full) Someone on the Show is a Former Scam Artist + Bobby Give His Top 5 Garth Songs + Lunchbox Gets Bad News from a Psychic
itunes:title: (Tues Full) Someone on the Show is a Former Scam Artist + Bobby Give His Top 5 Garth Songs + Lunchbox Gets Bad News from a Psychic
description:
Someone on the show used to be a scam artist, find out who and what they used to scam. After learning about the story behind "Thunder Rolls" yesterday, Bobby discusses his top 5 Garth Brooks songs of all time. Lunchbox calls a psychic and receives some bad news.
